==Swedish==
===Etymology===
Compound of ''[[handel]]'' (trade) and ''[[högskola]]'' ([[university college]].) 

===Noun===
{{sv-noun-reg-or|handelshögskol}}

#A [[university]] specialized in business administration and / or [[economics]].

====External links====
*[[w:University_college#Sweden|Wikipedia article on university colleges]].

====Usage note====
*Despite its name, a ''handelshögskola'' is a full-fledged university.

